title: Ep: 022 - Finding Early Success on Instagram
description: In this episode of Architecture, Design & Photography we sit down with Josh Johnson, Wedding Photographer and Founder of JJ Community, for a discussion around his early success with Instagram and his journey navigating the world of wedding photography.
